{"about_the_game":"This is a survivors-like game set in the backdrop of the Three Kingdoms era.  Players will step into the shoes of renowned generals from that period, grow through each battle, unleash the power of their martial spirit, constantly take on stronger foes, and ultimately conquer the three kingdoms.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/extras/top.gif?t=1737724598\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You can choose from nearly 20 renowned generals from the Three Kingdoms, each with their own unique abilities.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/extras/character.gif?t=1737724598\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">There are dozens of distinctive weapons to choose from, along with a special weapon upgrade system. Even a basic sword can be transformed into a powerful divine weapon.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/extras/weapon.gif?t=1737724598\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The battlefield is constantly changing, so try your best to dodge enemy attacks and carve a path through the opposing forces.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/extras/battle.gif?t=1737724598\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defeat enemies to gather resources, and use them to purchase weapons and equipment before the next wave of enemies arrives.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/extras/shop.gif?t=1737724598\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Embark on a conquest across the Three Kingdoms, overcome various challenges, and ultimately conquer the land.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/extras/map.gif?t=1737724598\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483670/pag